":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\">\n  <div class=\"notecard warning\" id=\"sect2\"><p><strong>非标准:</strong> 该特性是非标准的，请尽量不要在生产环境中使用它！</p></div></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"summary","title":"概述","isH3":false,"content":"<p><code><strong>toSource()</strong></code> 方法返回该对象源码的字符串表示。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">numObj.toSource();\nNumber.toSource();\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameters","title":"参数","isH3":true,"content":"<p>无</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"description","title":"描述","isH3":false,"content":"<p><code>toSource()</code> 方法返回下列值：</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li>对于内置&nbsp;<code>Number</code> 对象，&nbsp;<code>toSource()</code> 返回下面字符串，用来指明源码是不可见的。</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"eval notranslate\">function Number() { [native code] }</pre>\n<ul>\n <li>对于&nbsp;<code>Number</code>&nbsp;对象的实例，<code>toSource()</code> 返回一个表示源码的字符串。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>该方法通常被 JavaScript 内部调用，而不是在代码中显示调用。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"规范","title":"规范","isH3":false,"content":"<p>不是任何标准的一部分。在 JavaScript 1.3 被实现。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"浏览器兼容性","title":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"content":"{{Compat}}"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"相关链接","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toString\"><code>Object.prototype.toSource()</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"概述","id":"summary"},{"text":"语法","id":"syntax"},{"text":"描述","id":"description"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"相关链接","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"toSource() 方法返回该对象源码的字符串表示。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Number.prototype.toSource()","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Number.prototype.toSource()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Number.prototype.toSource()","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Portu